       pwd_context = CryptoContext(schemas=['argon2'],deprecated="auto") // this is new code where we are not defining any alogrithm or type it will take what is updated and lastest

       In Old Code We Write it as 

       pwd_context =  CryptoContext(schemas=['argon2'],"bcrypt","HS256") // In This We Are Defining What to use but if it get older then also our program should use it ..

