    4. Now in Our auth file we need to create a function for creating JWT Access Token
    5. Now In user.py modify login code after successfull login return JWT Token .
    6. Now We have to create verify token function for verifying token.
    7. Now We Have to import OAuth2PasswordBearer from fastapi.security for extracting token from header where user send it from request body header .
    8. Now create a get_current_user function to verify token and also found user is present or not as per flow you can see it . And it would be used for Applying Dependencies to other functions .
    9. To Lock The Functions To Not Be Able to use without login which dependcy injection as per seen in code .

