    2. In Easy And in my Words Relationship Mapping is nothing but just showing users data to that users only not other users data to other user .
    3. Basically in saas product their is multiple employees but which user added which employee is we get by using relationship mapping means while adding employee in database also insert added_by column in that inert user's id so its simple to fetch it by user.
    4. Now we are creating a simple column in task that is user_id where we store user_id who was added the task .
    5. We Will Apply Forgeion Key To That column and Foregion is primary key of user table id as you see in program okayy .
    6. Then we will apply filter to task crud opertion means while adding we add user_id also while update and delete and we will get user.id from dependcy that was current_user.




