8. What is react-router-dom And Why to use it ?
-> "React Router DOM helps us manage navigation between pages in a React application without reloading the browser."
    *** 
    What is DOM ?
    "DOM stands for Document Object Model. It represents an HTML page as a tree of objects, allowing JavaScript to read, update, and manipulate elements dynamically."

9. What is axios ?
-> Axios is a library for making HTTP requests, and we use it because it simplifies API communication and provides feature like interceptors and better error handling .



